Classes

class  IRasterPropertyDictionaryImp
 The FdoIRasterPropertyDictionary exposes a dictionary style interface to the raster properties. Through this interface the non-standard properties of a raster image can be determined and their values can be retrieved and set. Data values are exchanged through the FdoDataValue object to accommodate various data types, boolean, integer, double, string etc. More...
